data.description: Nestled in the quiet neighborhood of Meadow Vista Estates in Arlington you will find this one owner gem.  Well loved and maintained throughout this home is ready to move to call your own.  Four bedrooms means there is room for everyone in the family to have their own space.  A large kitchen overlooks the living room making conversation while cooking or entertaining easy.  The formal living room and dining room are perfect for all occasions.  Right in between everything Arlington and Mansfield has to offer means your a short ride to food, fun, and entertainment for all.  Welcome Home!
